des: Piratehead Radio sets sail and plans to bring you away with it to a paradise far away ruled by pirates, even if it is only in your mind. With roots based in Country, Rock & Reggae, it is a celebration of singer-songwriters well established and barely known, all the same. With new music being added daily, you can find your escape here with us!
